    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay, so if i just drink the juice on the days i *don't* take the pill, is that totally safe? like, if i skip my pill for a day to have the juice and then take it the next day, does that solve the problem? i don't want to miss a dose though if i don't have to.",
